      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  Midas - Standing Data Module                                 *
      *                                                               *
      *  SD0721P - Collateral Types Report                            *
      *                                                               *
      *  Function:  This program will generate a new report detailing *
      *             records in the Collateral Types File.  It will be *
      *             available on request in I/C/ and COB to produce a *
      *             full list of all collateral types on the system.  *
      *             It will also run automatically during COB to      *
      *             produce an audit list of all collateral types     *
      *             inserted, amended, or deleted that day.           *
