      *  CRE026 - Consumer Banking (Recompile)                        *
      *  CGL011 - Collateral Processing for Midas                     *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
     FSDCOTPL1IF  E           K        DISK
      ** Collateral Types File
      *
     FSDFCTLL0UF  E           K        DISK
      ** Standing Data Controls
      *
     FSD0721PAO   E                    PRINTER
     F                                              KINFDS SPOOLU
     FSD0721P1O   E                    PRINTER                        UC
     F                                              KINFDS SPOOL1
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  F U N C T I O N   O F   I N D I C A T O R S                  *
      *                                                               *
      *   20  - AUDIT or FULL Header                                  *
      *   21  - File out of Balance                                   *
      *   37  - Multibranching ON                                     *
      *   60  - READ Indicator for SDCOTPL1                           *
      *   61  - CHAIN Indicator for SDFCTLL0                          *
      *   98  - Date Format: DDMMYY (off); MMDDYY (on)                *
      * 90-99 - Used by Standard Subroutines                          *
      * U7+U8 - Database Error                                        *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      /SPACE 3
     E                    CPY@    1   1 80
      ** Array containing Copyright statement
      *
     E                    TXT     1   9  9
      ** Array containing Processing Type Texts
      *
     E                    MTD     1   4 11
      ** Array containing Revaluation Method Texts
      *
     E                    FRQ     1   8 10
      ** Array containing Revaluation Frequency Texts
      *
      /COPY ZSRSRC,ZDATE2Z1
      ** Array containing Conversion table for date
      *
      /COPY ZSRSRC,ZEDITZ1
      ** Array containing Conversion table for amount
      *
     ILDA       E DSLDA                         256
      ** Local data area for database error details
      *
     IRUNDAT    E DSRUNDAT
      ** Data Area giving Rundate
      *
     IPFMDS     ESDSY2PGDSP
      ** Program Status Data Structure
      *
     IINFDS$    E DSY2I$DSP
      ** Printer file information data structure.
      *
     ISPOOL1      DS
      ** File Information Data Structure for SD0721P1.
      *
     I                                       83  92 SFILE1
     I                                    B 123 1240SFNUM1
     I                                    B 188 1890OFLLN1
     I                                    B 367 3680PRTLN1
      *
     ISPOOLU      DS
      ** File Information Data Structure for SD0721PA.
      *
     I                                       83  92 SFILEU
     I                                    B 123 1240SFNUMU
      *
      ** Data Structure to format Date
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   7 FDAT1
     I                                        1   2 FDAY1
     I                                        3   5 FMON1
     I                                        6   7 FYER1
      *
      ** Data Structure to format Date
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   7 FDAT2
     I                                        1   3 FMON2
     I                                        4   5 FDAY2
     I                                        6   7 FYER2
      *
     ISDBANK    E DSSDBANKPD
      ** External data structures for Bank Details
      *
     IDSSDY     E DSDSSDY
      ** Long data structure for access objects
      *
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  S U B R O U T I N E   I N D E X                              *
      *                                                               *
      *  SRINIT - Program Initialisation                              *
      *  SRPROC - Main Processing Routine                             *
      *  SRREPT - Output Details to Report                            *
      *  SRDETL - Format and Write a Detail Record to the Report      *
      *  SRUPDT - Update Control File                                 *
      *  SR1END - Write End of Report                                 *
      *  SRAUDT - Output Audit Report and End Program                 *
      *  *PSSR  - Standard DB Error Processing                        *
      *  SRCFP1 - Register SD0721P1 via RCF                           *
      *  SRCFAU - Register SD0721PA via RCF                           *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *
      *================================================================
      *  P R O G R A M   S T A R T                                    *
      *================================================================
      *
      ** Perform Initialisation
      *
     C                     EXSR SRINIT
      *
      ** Perform Detail Processing
      *
     C                     EXSR SRPROC
      *
      ** Output Audit Report and End Program
      *
     C                     EXSR SRAUDT
      *
      *================================================================
      *  P R O G R A M   E N D                                        *
      *================================================================
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRINIT  -  Program Initialisation                            *
      *  Called By: Main Processing                                   *
      *  Calls    : AOBANKR0 - Access Bank Details                    *
      *             SRCFP1, SRCFAU                                    *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRINIT    BEGSR
      *
      ** Set up copyright parameter
      *
     C                     MOVEACPY@      CPY2@  80
      *
      ** Receive Parameter List
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PRTCD   7
     C                     PARM           PAURE   1
     C                     PARM           PRSEQ   5
     C                     PARM           PRLEV   1
     C                     PARM           PRENT   3
      *
      ** Initialise LDA field
      *
     C           *NAMVAR   DEFN           LDA
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     MOVEL'SD0721P' DBPGM
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   DBFILE
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   DBKEY
     C                     Z-ADD0         DBASE
     C                     OUT  LDA
      *
      ** Call Access Program for Bank Details
      *
     C                     CALL 'AOBANKR0'
     C                     PARM '*MSG   ' WRTCD   7
     C                     PARM '*FIRST ' WOPTN   7
     C           SDBANK    PARM SDBANK    DSSDY
      *
      ** Handle Database Error
      *
     C           WRTCD     IFNE *BLANKS
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     MOVEL'*FIRST  'DBKEY
     C                     MOVE 'SDBANKPD'DBFILE           ***************
     C                     Z-ADD001       DBASE            *DB ERROR 001 *
     C                     OUT  LDA                        ***************
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Check System Date Format, DDMMYY (*IN98 off)
      **                           MMDDYY (*IN98 on)
      *
     C           BJDFIN    IFEQ 'M'
     C                     MOVE '1'       *IN98
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Access RUNDAT for multibranching indicator
      *
     C           *NAMVAR   DEFN           RUNDAT
     C                     IN   RUNDAT
      *
     C           AGMBIN    IFEQ 'M'
     C                     MOVE '1'       *IN37
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Determine which header tp print
      *
     C           PAURE     IFEQ 'A'
     C                     MOVE '1'       *IN20
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** RCF Processing for Audit File
      *
     C                     EXSR SRCFAU
      *
      ** Report Work fields
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         RQDLN1  30
     C                     Z-ADD0         DIFLN1  30
     C                     Z-ADD0         STRTLN  30
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   WFIRST  1
      *
      ** Register SD0721P1 to RCF
      *
     C                     CLOSESD0721P1
     C                     OPEN SD0721P1
     C                     EXSR SRCFP1
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRPROC  -  Main Processing Routine                           *
      *  Called By: Main Processing                                   *
      *  Calls    : SRAUDT, SRREPT, SR1END, SRUPDT                    *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRPROC    BEGSR
      *
     C                     Z-ADDSTRTLN    PRTLN1
      *
      ** Establish starting position
      *
     C           *LOVAL    SETLLSDCOTPL1
      *
      ** Read Collateral Locations
      *
     C                     READ SDCOTPL1                 60
      *
     C           *IN60     IFEQ '1'
      *
      ** Generate SD0721PA to report no Collateral Locations found
      *
     C                     EXSR SRAUDT
     C                     ELSE
      *
     C           *IN60     DOUEQ'1'
      *
      ** Count records read
      *
     C                     ADD  1         RCOUNT
      *
      ** Process Report Lines
      *
     C                     EXSR SRREPT
      *
      ** Read next record
      *
     C                     READ SDCOTPL1                 60
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Write final records and Totals to Report
      *
     C                     EXSR SR1END
      *
      ** Update Control File
      *
     C                     EXSR SRUPDT
      *
      ** Blank out Return Code
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   PRTCD
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRREPT  -  Output Details to Report                          *
      *  Called By: SRPROC                                            *
      *  Calls    : ZEDIT, ZDATE2, SRDETL                             *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRREPT    BEGSR
      *
     C                     CLEARDETAIL
      *
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       W0PFM   1
      *
      ** Skip records not accessed today if Audit List is requested
      *
     C           PAURE     IFEQ 'A'
     C           CTLCD     ANDNEBJRDNB
     C                     MOVE 'N'       W0PFM
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Format Details of Report
      *
     C           W0PFM     IFEQ 'Y'
      *
      ** Collateral Type
      *
     C                     MOVELCTCOLT    RCOLT
      *
      ** Collateral Type Description
      *
     C                     MOVELCTCOLD    RCOLD
      *
      ** Collateral Processing Type
      *
     C                     SELEC
     C           CTCOPT    WHEQ 'A'                        Account
     C                     MOVELTXT,1     RCOPT
     C           CTCOPT    WHEQ 'C'                        Charge
     C                     MOVELTXT,2     RCOPT
     C           CTCOPT    WHEQ 'D'                        Deposit
     C                     MOVELTXT,3     RCOPT
     C           CTCOPT    WHEQ 'G'                        Guarantee
     C                     MOVELTXT,4     RCOPT
     C           CTCOPT    WHEQ 'H'                        Holding
     C                     MOVELTXT,5     RCOPT
     C           CTCOPT    WHEQ 'L'                        Letter
     C                     MOVELTXT,6     RCOPT
     C           CTCOPT    WHEQ 'M'                        Mortgage
     C                     MOVELTXT,7     RCOPT
     C           CTCOPT    WHEQ 'O'                        Official Guarantee
     C                     MOVELTXT,8     RCOPT
     C           CTCOPT    WHEQ 'P'                        Pledge
     C                     MOVELTXT,9     RCOPT
     C                     ENDSL
      *
      ** Default Margin
      *
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   ZFIELD
     C                     MOVE CTMPCT    ZFIELD
     C                     Z-ADD2         ZADEC
     C                     EXSR ZEDIT
     C                     MOVE ZFIELD    RMPCT
      *
      ** Retention Period
      *
     C                     MOVELCTRTNP    RRTNP
      *
      ** Revaluation Method
      *
     C                     SELEC
     C           CTRVLM    WHEQ 'D'                        Daily Automatic Update
     C                     MOVELMTD,1     RRVLM
     C           CTRVLM    WHEQ 'M'                        Manual Revaluation
     C                     MOVELMTD,2     RRVLM
     C           CTRVLM    WHEQ 'P'                        Regular Application of Price Feed
     C                     MOVELMTD,3     RRVLM
     C           CTRVLM    WHEQ 'R'                        Restatement of Collateral Value
     C                     MOVELMTD,4     RRVLM
     C                     ENDSL
      *
      ** Revaluation Date
      *
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   FDAT1
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   FDAT2
     C                     Z-ADD0         ZDAYNO
     C                     MOVE CTRVLD    ZDAYNO
     C                     EXSR ZDATE2
     C                     MOVELZADATE    RRVLD
      *
      ** Reformat date if *IN98 is *ON
      *
     C           *IN98     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVELZADATE    FDAT1
     C                     MOVELFDAY1     FDAY2
     C                     MOVELFMON1     FMON2
     C                     MOVELFYER1     FYER2
     C                     MOVELFDAT2     RRVLD
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Revaluation Frequency
      *
     C                     SELEC
     C           CTRVLF    WHEQ 'D'                        Daily
     C                     MOVELFRQ,1     RRVLF
     C           CTRVLF    WHEQ 'W'                        Weekly
     C                     MOVELFRQ,2     RRVLF
     C           CTRVLF    WHEQ 'F'                        Forthnightly
     C                     MOVELFRQ,3     RRVLF
     C           CTRVLF    WHEQ 'M'                        Monthly
     C                     MOVELFRQ,4     RRVLF
     C           CTRVLF    WHEQ 'T'                        Every Two Months
     C                     MOVELFRQ,5     RRVLF
     C           CTRVLF    WHEQ 'Q'                        Quarterly
     C                     MOVELFRQ,6     RRVLF
     C           CTRVLF    WHEQ 'X'                        Six Monthly
     C                     MOVELFRQ,7     RRVLF
     C           CTRVLF    WHEQ 'Y'                        Yearly
     C                     MOVELFRQ,8     RRVLF
     C                     ENDSL
      *
      ** Revaluation Day Number
      *
     C                     MOVELCTRVLN    RRVLN
      *
      ** Last Change Date
      *
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   FDAT1
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   FDAT2
     C                     Z-ADD0         ZDAYNO
     C                     MOVE CTLCD     ZDAYNO
     C                     EXSR ZDATE2
     C                     MOVELZADATE    RLCD
      *
      ** Reformat date if *IN98 is *ON
      *
     C           *IN98     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVELZADATE    FDAT1
     C                     MOVELFDAY1     FDAY2
     C                     MOVELFMON1     FMON2
     C                     MOVELFYER1     FYER2
     C                     MOVELFDAT2     RLCD
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Last Change Type
      *
     C                     SELEC
     C           CTTYLC    WHEQ 'I'
     C                     MOVEL'Insert'  RTYLC
     C           CTTYLC    WHEQ 'A'
     C                     MOVEL'Amend'   RTYLC
     C           CTTYLC    WHEQ 'D'
     C                     MOVEL'Delete'  RTYLC
     C                     ENDSL
      *
      ** Write out the record
      *
     C                     EXSR SRDETL
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRDETL  -  Format and Write a Detail Record to the Report    *
      *  Called By: SRREPT                                            *
      *  Calls    : None                                              *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRDETL    BEGSR
      *
      ** Check that sufficient lines remain for the Format. If not,
      ** write out the Main Headings on a new page.
      *
     C                     Z-ADD1         RQDLN1
     C           OFLLN1    SUB  PRTLN1    DIFLN1
     C           DIFLN1    IFLE RQDLN1
     C                     WRITEHEADP1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Write out Detail Record
      *
     C                     WRITEDETAIL
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRUPDT  -  Update Control File                               *
      *  Called By: SRPROC                                            *
      *  Calls    : None                                              *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRUPDT    BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVEL'SDCOTPPD'KFILE  10
     C           KFILE     CHAINSDFCTLL0             61
      *
     C           *IN61     IFEQ '1'
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     MOVELKFILE     DBKEY
     C                     MOVE 'SDFCTLPA'DBFILE           ***************
     C                     Z-ADD002       DBASE            *DB ERROR 002 *
     C                     OUT  LDA                        ***************
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE AHNOIN    RINSER
     C                     MOVE AHNOAM    RAMEND
     C                     MOVE AHNODL    RDELET
     C                     MOVE AHNORC    RAUDIT
     C                     Z-ADD0         AHNOIN
     C                     Z-ADD0         AHNOAM
     C                     Z-ADD0         AHNODL
     C                     UPDAT@AHREAU
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SR1END  -  Write End of Report                               *
      *  Called By: SRPROC                                            *
      *  Calls    : None                                              *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SR1END    BEGSR
      *
      ** Check that sufficient lines remain for the Format. If not,
      ** write out the Main Headings on a new page.
      *
     C                     Z-ADD4         RQDLN1
     C           OFLLN1    SUB  PRTLN1    DIFLN1
     C           DIFLN1    IFLE RQDLN1
     C                     WRITEHEADP1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Write out Total Format
      *
     C                     WRITETRAILP1
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRAUDT  -  Output Audit Report and End Program               *
      *  Called By: Main Processing, SRPROC, *PSSR                    *
      *  Calls    : None                                              *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRAUDT    BEGSR
      *
      ** Output Report Header and File Controls.
      *
     C                     WRITEHEADAU
      *
      ** If there is a DB Error, Output the DB Error Information
      *
     C           *INU7     IFEQ '1'
     C                     WRITEDBERROR
     C                     MOVEL'*ERROR ' PRTCD
     C                     ELSE
      *
      ** Determine if there is file out of balance
      *
     C           RCOUNT    IFNE RAUDIT
     C                     MOVE '1'       *IN21
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     WRITECONTROL
      *
      ** Or, if no records read, Output "No Details" message
      *
     C           RCOUNT    IFEQ 0
     C                     WRITENODTLS
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** End Program and Return
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  *PSSR   -  Standard DB Error processing                      *
      *  Called By: SRINIT, SRREPT                                    *
      *  Calls    : SRAUDT                                            *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           *PSSR     BEGSR
      *
      ** Check to see that *PSSR has not already been called
      *
     C           WRUN      IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WRUN    1
     C                     SETON                     U7U8
     C                     DUMP
     C                     EXSR SRAUDT
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** If *PSSR already run, then just end the program here
      *
     C                     SETON                     U7U8LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRCFP1  -  Register SD0721P1 via RCF                         *
      *  Called By: SRINIT                                            *
      *  Calls    : ZSFILE                                            *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRCFP1    BEGSR
      *
      ** Ensure Report Spool File recorded by RCF
      *
     C                     Z-ADDSFNUM1    ZSNUM   60
      *
     C                     CALL 'ZSFILE'
     C**********           PARM *BLANKS   SEQ     5                                           241674
     C**********           PARM           SENTY   3                                           241674
     C**********           PARM           SFILE1                                              241674
     C**********           PARM           ZSNUM                                               241674
     C                     PARM PRSEQ     SEQ     5                                           241674
     C                     PARM PRENT     SENTY   3                                           241674
     C                     PARM SFILE1    SFILE1                                              241674
     C                     PARM SFNUM1    ZSNUM                                               241674
     C                     PARM           ZSERR   1
      *
      ** If Error occurs during ZSFILE processing, then return to the
      ** Calling Program
      *
     C           ZSERR     IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     SETON                     U7U8LR
     C                     RETRN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           WFIRST    IFNE 'Y'
     C                     Z-ADDPRTLN1    STRTLN
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WFIRST
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRCFAU  -  Register SD0721PA via RCF                         *
      *  Called By: SRINIT                                            *
      *  Calls    : ZSFILE                                            *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRCFAU    BEGSR
      *
      ** Ensure Audit Spool File recorded by RCF
      *
     C                     Z-ADDSFNUMU    ZSNUMU  60
      *
     C                     CALL 'ZSFILE'
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   SEQ
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   SENTY
     C                     PARM           SFILEU
     C                     PARM           ZSNUMU
     C                     PARM *BLANK    ZSERR
      *
      ** If Error occurs during ZSFILE processing, then return to the
      ** Calling Program
      *
     C           ZSERR     IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     SETON                     U7U8LR
     C                     RETRN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      /EJECT
